         <abstract id="aspace_74f04c9eb4a14d87c12f18f2aabea046">An artificial collection of volumes, tracts, deeds, and clippings on the topic of slavery. A seven volume composition of material on slavery and abolition, and a "Census of the Slaves in Chester County, Pennsylvania" are included.</abstract>
    
      </did>
